OL,7,FTaxi driver Urfan Sharif, 42, made the
OL,8,Fadmission as his wife Beinash Batool,
OL,9,F30, sobbed in the dock of the Old
OL,10,FBailey on Wednesday.
OL,12,FPreviously, Sharif had sought to blame
OL,13,FBatool for killing his daughter but on
OL,14,FWednesday told jurors: "I accept every
OL,15,Fsingle thing."
OL,17,FSara was found dead at the family home
OL,18,Fin Woking, Surrey, on August 10 2023
OL,19,Fafter the defendants fled to Pakistan.
