OL,7,FCross-examining for his wife, Caroline
OL,8,FCarberry KC asked Sharif about a note
OL,9,Fhe left beside the body of his
OL,10,Fdaughter before leaving for Pakistan.
OL,12,FIn it, he wrote "love you Sara" on the
OL,13,Ffirst page followed by the words:
OL,14,F"Whoever see this note it's me Urfan
OL,15,FSharif who killed my daughter by
OL,16,Fbeating."
OL,18,FMs Carberry asked if he did indeed
OL,19,Fkill his daughter by beating and
OL,20,FSharif replied: "Yes, she died because
OL,21,Fof me."
